import React from 'react'
import{Nav,NavbarContainer,NavLogo} from './Nav'
import {FaBars} from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
       <Nav>
         <NavbarContainer>
             <NavLogo to='/'>
              dolla
             </NavLogo>
             <MobileIcon>
                 <FaBars/>
             </MobileIcon>
             <NavMenu>
                 <NavItem>
                     <NavLinks to='about'>
                         About
                     </NavLinks>
                 </NavItem>
             </NavMenu>
         </NavbarContainer>
       </Nav>
       </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
